al; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Do you charge for delivery?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;The minimum\r\norder value is INR 1500 for free delivery.. In case you do not reach the limit,\r\na delivery charge will be levied against that order.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Order\r\nValue&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\nDelivery Charge&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Less than\r\nRs. 1500&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;60&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Above\r\nRs.1500&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;\r\nFREE&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;How can I make changes to my order before and\r\nafter confirmation?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;You can edit\r\nyour products in the cart before checkout. If you’ve already placed an order,\r\nyou can cancel and reorder it, with the required list. &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;How can I be sure the fruits and vegetables I\r\norder are of good quality?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Our fruits\r\nand vegetables vendors have a quality check process in place to ensure quality\r\nof the items delivered is up to the mark. Do let us know within 24 Hours if\r\nyou’re not happy with the quality of the product received&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;How will I know if any item in my order is\r\nunavailable?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;You will\r\nreceive an SMS notification or a Call from Naani’s Supermart informing you\r\nabout the unavailable items in this situation.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;How can I make payments at Naani’s Supermart?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;Naani”s\r\nSupermart accepts only cash on delivery (COD).Other modes are available before\r\n1&lt;sup&gt;st&lt;/sup&gt; January.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;What If I want to return something?&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(128, 130, 133); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;If you’re\r\ndissatisfied with the products delivered, please register a complaint at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:support@naanissupermart.com&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;support@naanissupermart.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 8.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt; &amp;nbsp;within 24 hours for non-perishable items and 12 hours for perishable items. Our\r\ncustomer support team will get in touch with you to resolve this issue.You can\r\nalso return the products which you are dissatisfied with, at the time of\r\ndelivery.&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'About Us', '', ''),
(8, 1, 'Careers', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;It’s an audacious, incredibly rewarding mission that our increasingly diverse team is dedicated to achieving.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Naani\'s Supermart is built around the idea that everyone should be able to meet all the basic needs, including Grocery, Personal care items, Household care, etc. To that end, we aim to empower people of&amp;nbsp; j&amp;amp;K to experience online shopping with us in a beter way.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.naanissupermart.in/index.php?route=information/contact&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Join us&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;in this journey of serving a new and better shopping experience to the people of J&amp;amp;K.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Send your CV at : HR@naanissupermart.in&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Cereal, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;call / WhatsApp :&amp;nbsp;8899-87-9988&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Career', '', '');
