(60, 1, 'Fortune Rozana  Basmati Rice 5KG', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Celias, Helvetica; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;To enjoy a perfect plate of rice, Fortune Rozana Basmati rice is an ideal choice. It has slender, long grains that taste delicious after cooking. The rice grains imparts an enticing aroma to all your dishes. Perfect basmati rice for daily use. It is packed in a hygienic way. Rice does not stick together after cooking. Contains Vitamin B-complex, dietary fibre, iron, folate, and magnesium to keep your body healthy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Fortune Rozana  Basmati Rice 5KG', '', ''),
