(63, 1, 'Fortune  Soya Health  Oil  Pouch 1L', '&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Fortified with the goodness of Vitamins A and D&lt;br&gt;Light, odourless and healthy oil&lt;br&gt;Helps in keeping your heart healthy&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;--------------Enriched with Omega 3 fatty acids, the Fortune Soya Health Refined Soyabean Oil is one of the best cooking mediums when it comes to baking sweets and cakes. The oil has a neutral flavour and is odourless and well as healthy. This oil is fortified with the rich goodness of Vitamin A and Vitamin D that keeps the eyes and bones healthy. It is a lightweight and odourless oil that makes it a great choice for keeping the heart healthy. It is an ideal oil for baking, sauteing and stir frying.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Fortune  Soya Health  Oil  Pouch 1L', '', ''),
(65, 1, 'Fortune Soya Health Refined Soyabean Oil (Tin) 15 KG', '&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Fortified with the goodness of Vitamins A and D&lt;br&gt;Light, odourless and healthy oil&lt;br&gt;Helps in keeping your heart healthy&lt;br&gt;Ideal for baking, sautéing and stir frying&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;-----------------Make the healthy choice for a healthy heart by using Fortune Soya Health Refined Soyabean Oil for cooking, It is a light oil that that provides the goodness of soybeans in every bite, The food prepared in it absorbs less oil, and it is hence a healthy cooking medium, It has the goodness of Vitamins A, D, and E, Keeps your heart healthy as it is free from bad cholesterol, Perfect for all baking, sautéing, and stir-frying needs.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Fortune Soya Health Refined Soyabean Oil (Tin) 15 KG', '', ''),
