(146, 1, 'Tata Sampann Kabuli Chana Bold 1KG', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Celias, Helvetica; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Try new recipes and make flavourful and exotic dishes with the Tata Sampann Kabuli Chana. Packaged using 5-step purity process, this chana is cleaner, uniform and superior. Kubali Chana is rich in protein making it a very good daily staple. Unpolished dal which does not undergo any artificial processing with water, leather or oil. Imparts a creamy taste and texture&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Tata Sampanna Kabuli Chana Bold 1KG', '', ''),
