(147, 1, 'Tata Sampann Kala Chana 1KG', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Celias, Helvetica; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Tata Sampann Kala Chana contains premium-quality carefully sourced grains with a rich flavour. Packed using 5-step purity process, this chana is cleaner, uniform and superior. It is rich in protein making it unmissable for vegetarians and vegans. Good source of fiber and iron, helps improve digestion and blood circulation. Irresistibly tasty, Tata Sampann Kala Chana is an unpolished pulse that has a creamy texture.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Tata Sampanna Kala Chana 1KG', '', ''),
