(571, 1, 'Dabur Gulabari Face Freshener Spray, 100 ml', '&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#111111&quot; face=&quot;Amazon Ember, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Featyres&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#111111&quot; face=&quot;Amazon Ember, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini&quot; style=&quot;margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 18px; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); padding: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;Cleanses, refreshes &amp;amp; cools the skin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;Effective for all skin types&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;Directions for use: Spray Dabur Gulabari Rose Face Cleanser directly on your face &amp;amp; gently wipe your face with a cotton ball&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;First Aid measures in case of Itchiness, Eye exposure: Irrigate immediately with copious quantities of water for several minutes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;Skin testing for allergies - Procedure: Apply a small quantity of the product on the forearm &amp;amp; leave for few minutes. If the skin becomes red &amp;amp; appears itchy, you may be allergic to the product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;For sensitive, problem-prone skin, use of regular skin care products may be the root cause of your problems. Dabur Gulabari Face Cleanser is a gentle face cleanser which allows you to reap the natural anti-inflammatory benefits of rose water for your skin while cleansing it from deep. It is safe and effective for all skin types.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Every effort is made to maintain accuracy of all information. However, actual product packaging and materials may contain more and/or different information. It is recommended not to solely rely on the information presented.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Dabur Gulabari Face Freshener Spray, 100 ml', '', ''),
(191, 1, 'Aashirvaad Chakki Atta 10KG', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: optima; font-size: 14px; width: 525px;&quot;&gt;At&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;title-fonts-changes&quot; style=&quot;font-family: agartitle !important; text-transform: uppercase !important;&quot;&gt;AASHIRVAAD&lt;/span&gt;, extra care is taken to keep things as natural as possible. The way Mother Nature intended for them to be. In our quest to provide you wholesome goodness, whole wheat grains are sourced, directly from the farmers.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: optima; font-size: 14px; width: 525px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;title-fonts-changes&quot; style=&quot;font-family: agartitle !important; text-transform: uppercase !important;&quot;&gt;AASHIRVAAD&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Whole Wheat Atta was launched on 27th May 2002 and now has become the number one in branded packaged atta across the country.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: optima; font-size: 14px; width: 525px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;title-fonts-changes&quot; style=&quot;font-family: agartitle !important; text-transform: uppercase !important;&quot;&gt;AASHIRVAAD&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Whole Wheat Atta is made from the grains which are heavy on the palm, golden amber in colour and hard in bite. It is carefully ground using modern \'chakki - grinding\' process which ensures that&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;title-fonts-changes&quot; style=&quot;font-family: agartitle !important; text-transform: uppercase !important;&quot;&gt;AASHIRVAAD&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Atta contains 0% Maida and is 100% Sampoorna Atta. Thus we ensure you get superior chakki atta, through our 4 Step Advantage process of sourcing, cleaning, grinding and nutrition lockage.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: optima; font-size: 14px; width: 525px;&quot;&gt;By ensuring that all the nutrients of the grain stay intact and protected in our packaging, we deliver the freshness of the fields combined with the power of the whole wheat.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 10px; font-family: optima; font-size: 14px; width: 525px;&quot;&gt;The dough made from&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;title-fonts-changes&quot; style=&quot;font-family: agartitle !important; text-transform: uppercase !important;&quot;&gt;AASHIRVAAD&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;Atta absorbs more water, hence rotis remain softer for longer. This means you serve soft, fluffy rotis to your family which powers them through their day!&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Aashirvaad Chakki Atta 10KG', '', ''),
