ber&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Every effort is made to maintain accuracy of all information. However, actual product packaging and materials may contain more and/or different information. It is recommended not to solely rely on the information presented.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Tresemme Hairfall Defence Conditioner , 190 ml', '', ''),
