(79, 1, 'Saffola Active Pro Weight Watchers Blended Cooking Oil (Pouch) 1L', '&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Saffola Active, Pro-weight Watchers, edible oil is a unique blend of 80% refined rice bran oil and 20% soybean oil&lt;br&gt;Dual Seed Technology: Gives you the goodness of two oils in one.&lt;br&gt;Saffola Active blended cooking oil has the combined benefits of Antioxidants and LOSORB Technology.&lt;br&gt;Since the quantity of oil consumed every day is as important as the right quality of oil you choose for daily cooking, Saffola Active, blended edible oil, helps you ensure both.&lt;br&gt;Fortified with Vitamin A, D which helps against night blindness and supports strong bones&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;----------Saffola Active blended edible oil has the combined benefits of Antioxidants and LOSORB™ technology. Comes with Losorb Technology which results in upto 27%*lesser oil absorption in comparison to commonly consumed edible oils, hence leading to a healthier choice. Since quantity of oil consumed every day is as important as the quality of oil you choose for daily cooking, Saffola Active blended cooking oil helps you ensure both. Fortified with Vitamin A, D which helps against night blindness and supports strong bones.&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Saffola Active Pro Weight Watchers Blended Cooking Oil (Pouch) 1L', '', ''),
(470, 1, 'Saffola Gold Pro Healthy Lifestyle Blended Cooking Oil (Pouch) 1 L', '&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Blend of 70% refined rice bran oil and 30% refined sunflower oil&lt;br&gt;MUFA and PUFA: Saffola Gold edible oil has a good balance of MUFA &amp;amp; PUFA as advised by NIN/ICMR.&lt;br&gt;Dual Seed Technology: Gives you the goodness of two oils in one.&lt;br&gt;LOSORB Technology: Results in upto 35%* lesser oil absorption in your fried food&lt;br&gt;Contains the power of natural antioxidants that helps reduce free radicals and thus helps keeps your heart healthy.&lt;br&gt;Fortified with Vitamin A, D which helps against night blindness and supports strong bones&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;--------Comes with the benefits of oryzanol, natural Antioxidant, MUFA PUFA balance and Vitamins A and D. Offers improved nutritional profile. Saffola Gold edible oil comes with Losorb Technology which results in upto 35%*lesser oil absorption in comparison to commonly consumed edible oils and hence a healthier choice. Fortified with Vitamin A, D which helps against night blindness and supports strong bones.&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Saffola Gold Pro Healthy Lifestyle Blended Cooking Oil (Pouch) 1 L', '', ''),
