nce as well as germ kill.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;a-list-item&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-top: 0em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;Regular use of Harpic toilet cleaner prevents the build-up of stains in the toilet bowl and keeps it visibly clean with effective removal of germs in the toilet. Harpic Power Plus is available in various sizes and fragrances including: Original, Orange and Rose. Harpic’s strategically bent bottleneck shape lets you pour the liquid into deep corners under the toilet rim, without letting your hands touch giving you all round cleaning.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;padding: 0px; margin-top: 0em; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--name&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;Disclaimer&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;product-attribute__attr--description&quot; style=&quot;border-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.67; margin-top: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-family: Celias, Helvetica;&quot;&gt;Every effort is made to maintain accuracy of all information. However, actual product packaging and materials may contain more and/or different information. It is recommended not to solely rely on the information presented.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;dpx-aplus-product-description_feature_div&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: &amp;quot;Amazon Ember&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;div id=&quot;aplus_feature_d